  "_comment_secrets": "For Fase 5 (HTTPBackend / Cloud Function connectors) keep 'context' empty: secrets live in Secret Manager under 'client_<tenant_id>_<platform>_<key>' and the CF resolves them with its own SA. Only LocalBackend / dev mode needs credentials inline.",
  "_comment_security": "NEVER commit a populated tenants.json. It is gitignored at config/tenants.json. If real credentials end up here, rotate them.",
